},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.set","typeVersion":3.4,"position":[3618,1420],"id":"db97358c-ee14-44f4-9beb-01cc426c1b77","name":"Capture Failure Context"},{"parameters":{"select":"channel","channelId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"name","value":"#docs","cachedResultName":"#docs"},"text":"=🚨 {{ $json.workflow }} failed at {{ $json.failedNode }}: {{ $json.errorMessage }}","otherOptions":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.slack","typeVersion":2.3,"position":[3942,1420],"id":"d6083b1e-b6cb-4256-94a5-22f1c0e54d7d","name":"Escalate Failure to Slack","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000},{"parameters":{"content":"### Daily Schedule\n\nStarts the workflow on a timer — daily at 17:00. No input data; downstream nodes fetch what they need.\n\nNext: Export All Rows (Google Sheets)","width":280,"height":232,"color":5},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-330,520],"id":"9487cba4-33ea-b6ed-bad8-dd8c7bf6780b","name":"Note: Daily Schedule"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Export All Rows (Google Sheets)\n\ngoogleSheets — `read` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Serialize to CSV · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-6,520],"id":"ff3220e6-f39a-46ae-a194-6c2a096de3e9","name":"Note: Export All Rows (Google Sheets)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Serialize to CSV\n\nSerializes items to a CSV binary file.\n\nNext: Compress Archive","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[318,520],"id":"d7e78911-ddbf-2049-406a-dff947d3fab6","name":"Note: Serialize to CSV"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Compress Archive\n\nZips the binary to cut storage/transfer size before upload.\n\nNext: Upload Backup to Google Drive","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[642,520],"id":"a76c74e1-4a10-3178-2a73-f164547e62f5","name":"Note: Compress Archive"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Upload Backup to Google Drive\n\ngoogleDrive — `upload` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Backup Size Sane? · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[966,520],"id":"d08b4037-0fa2-84d3-c676-10d502b02d9d","name":"Note: Upload Backup to Google Drive"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Backup Size Sane?\n\nTwo-way gate on `={{ ($binary.data?.fileSize ?? 1) > 0 }}`. TRUE continues the happy path, FALSE takes the alternate branch.\n\nPorts: ①→ Align Field Names · ②→ Alarm — Empty Backup","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1290,520],"id":"21f5c8c2-13d0-1b68-c1b8-afc3a2da4473","name":"Note: Backup Size Sane?"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Alarm — Empty Backup\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1614,1000],"id":"0481303e-4f18-48c0-155a-a8f9b8a08e7a","name":"Note: Alarm — Empty Backup"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Align Field Names\n\nNormalizes field names so every source feeds the same downstream schema.\n\nNext: Tag Pipeline Metadata","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1938,520],"id":"97ca42c0-9dca-de9d-c04e-899ed8a22d0d","name":"Note: Align Field Names"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Tag Pipeline Metadata\n\nShapes the item: writes `pipeline`, `version`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Cap Batch Volume","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2262,520],"id":"a34ff8f1-9534-54ff-f5e7-fb361fe57090","name":"Note: Tag Pipeline Metadata"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Cap Batch Volume\n\nCaps the stream at 100 items to protect downstream quotas.\n\nNext: Stamp Processing Time","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2586,520],"id":"691e3d0e-7d3a-245d-100b-7998794d920f","name":"Note: Cap Batch Volume"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Stamp Processing Time\n\nStamps `processedAt` with the current time for auditing.\n\nNext: Sort Documents Newest First","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2910,520],"id":"11c56327-9308-ee1d-42b5-9879e6eaeab1","name":"Note: Stamp Processing Time"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Sort Documents Newest First\n\nOrders items (newest first) so limits and digests pick the most relevant records.\n\nNext: Summarize Run Stats","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3234,520],"id":"337dae31-c663-b880-0da9-e0e0e22107b0","name":"Note: Sort Documents Newest First"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Summarize Run Stats\n\nShapes the item: writes `runAt`, `itemCount`, `status`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3558,520],"id":"b8769a41-12e7-2df1-f49d-f37aafef07d0","name":"Note: Summarize Run Stats"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)\n\ngoogleSheets — `append` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Send Summary to Slack · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3882,520],"id":"2d204b65-fde2-ad16-82ff-14dfa7dbe953","name":"Note: Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Send Summary to Slack\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4206,520],"id":"f74173fc-7982-ec75-e707-b284f44f71cf","name":"Note: Send Summary to Slack"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Capture Failure Context\n\nShapes the item: writes `failedNode`, `errorMessage`, `workflow`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Escalate Failure to Slack","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3558,1540],"id":"50811102-507a-1c01-0317-c383ac647a76","name":"Note: Capture Failure Context"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Escalate Failure to Slack\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3882,1540],"id":"cd73470a-4e18-e270-cd2e-0acbead4e618","name":"Note: Escalate Failure to Slack"},{"parameters":{"content":"# Parse documents with Google Drive with instant alerts\n\n**Pattern:** File Processing · **Level:** Advanced · **Trigger:** Scheduled\n\n## What it does\nParse documents with Google Drive with instant alerts. It runs automatically on a schedule.\n\n## Why it exists\nManual ocr & extraction is slow and error-prone; this workflow makes the process repeatable, monitored and hands-off, with failures surfaced instead of silently lost.\n\n## Main flow\nDaily Schedule → Export All Rows (Google Sheets) → Serialize to CSV → Compress Archive → Upload Backup to Google Drive → Backup Size Sane? → Align Field Names → …\n\n## Use it for\n- Teams that want to file processing without manual effort\n- Anyone automating ocr & extraction in legal\n- Replacing a fragile manual process with a reliable workflow\n\n## You get\n- Responds in seconds\n- Runs 24/7 in the background\n- Standardizes the process every time\n\n## Before first run\nConnect credentials: Google OAuth2; Google OAuth2 / service account; Slack OAuth2.\nFollow the color key: 🟦 entry · 🟪 AI · 🟫 actions · ⬜ utilities · 🟩 outputs · 🟥 error rail.\nEach node has its own doc card underneath — read those before editing.","width":480,"height":900},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-830,80],"id":"a32001f5-5582-2111-afb2-59a5f882109e","name":"📘 Workflow Overview"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛟 Error handling & retries\n\nExternal calls retry **3× with 2s backoff**. Anything still failing exits through its node's error output into the red error rail → context is captured and the on-call channel is alerted. Set an n8n **Error Workflow** in settings as the final safety net.","width":360,"height":260,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-230,-20],"id":"d74e9ff9-0c76-1233-7786-ae4fad2702a2","name":"🛟 Error handling & retries"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛠 Customize me\n\nQuick wins: point the data nodes at your own accounts (see 🔑 lines on each card), adjust the trigger cadence, and tune thresholds/labels to your ocr & extraction process. Every node card explains its role — safe to extend at any marked branch.","width":360,"height":260,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[190,-20],"id":"6f5a3575-7aec-e6f5-b74f-c1e769dba895","name":"🛠 Customize me"}],"connections":{"Daily Schedule":{"main":[[{"node":"Export All Rows (Google Sheets)","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Export All Rows (Google Sheets)":{"main":[[{"node":"Serialize to CSV","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Serialize to CSV":{"main":[[{"node":"Compress Archive","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Compress Archive":{"main":[[{"node":"Upload Backup to Google Drive","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Upload Backup to Google Drive":{"main":[[{"node":"Backup Size Sane?","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Backup Size Sane?":{"main":[[{"node":"Align Field Names","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Alarm — Empty Backup","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Align Field Names":{"main":[[{"node":"Tag Pipeline Metadata","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Tag Pipeline Metadata":{"main":[[{"node":"Cap Batch Volume","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Cap Batch Volume":{"main":[[{"node":"Stamp Processing Time","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Stamp Processing Time":{"main":[[{"node":"Sort Documents Newest First","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Sort Documents Newest First":{"main":[[{"node":"Summarize Run Stats","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Summarize Run Stats":{"main":[[{"node":"Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)":{"main":[[{"node":"Send Summary to Slack","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Capture Failure Context":{"main":[[{"node":"Escalate Failure to Slack","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Alarm — Empty Backup":{"main":[[],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Send Summary to Slack":{"main":[[],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]}},"active":false,"settings":{"executionOrder":"v1"},"meta":{"templateCredsSetupCompleted":false},"tags":[],"pinData":{},"versionId":"f6324ab1-1bb2-4242-8fff-1224d9af7254","id":"FDX03817"}